 3ï¸âƒ£ Authentication vs Authorization (Interview Favorite)

| Authentication          | Authorization     |
| ----------------------- | ----------------- |
| Identity verify         | Permission verify |
| Pehle hota hai          | Baad me hota hai  |
| Login related           | Action related    |
| Username, password, MFA | IAM Policy        |

---

